{"tid":721634,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[電][HD] 把握最後機會 港大師兄帶你過三爆四","createTime":"2018-06-28T21:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T08:28:33.000Z","uid":14170,"like":9,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"eabea5f36c29778b8ea747fa1c6515d901eb41c9","tid":721634,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T21:34:54.000Z","msg":"各位同學你地好，又係我鏗哥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鏗哥係 IVE EE 2014 屆畢業生，HKU EE 2018 畢業生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經幫 IVE 師弟補左四年，當中超過一半學生上返三大，最老個班學生已經升 year3 了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n補習既科目包括哂 EE ME BSE 嘅電 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩星期內我可以幫你由唔合格 -&gt; 合格，由 C -&gt; A <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nEE HD:<br />\nElectrical Installation<br />\nElectrical Power Systems<br />\nElectrical Machines and Drives<br />\n<br />\nME HD:<br />\nInstrumentation and Measurement<br />\nElectrical Technology<br />\n<br />\nBSE HD:<br />\nElectrical Installations B<br />\n<br />\n有需要既同學可以 telegram 搵我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/eetutor2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Feetutor2018&d=KvnPWttykP1zvNq6BdyG%2FdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b56d5489\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/eetutor2018</a><br />\n<br />\n最後祝校園台既各位考試順利，平安合格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0848301e5ad576d2bc5c874cf575a114798a4d01","tid":721634,"uid":51848,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T21:35:36.000Z","msg":"年經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鏗哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4512b429f56180e1ea6aeba01e0f1c1afd4831a0","tid":721634,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T21:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/053648_309d32bcc32ef7ae7afb3617e2e16006.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F053648_309d32bcc32ef7ae7afb3617e2e16006.png&h=3db7e4f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀左超過 30 科，我自己就 3B 全 A <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲未計呢幾年教左幾多學生拎 A <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70db0d67be4e2c97cab29f158e071ba268988deb","tid":721634,"uid":14170,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0848301e5ad576d2bc5c874cf575a114798a4d01","tid":721634,"uid":51848,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T21:35:36.000Z","msg":"年經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鏗哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T21:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa8389417ce8ba652d2db3debd4965a28fd1436","tid":721634,"uid":14170,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T21:40:26.000Z","msg":"最後兩星期 得返鏗哥幫到你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/eetutor2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Feetutor2018&d=KvnPWttykP1zvNq6BdyG%2FdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b56d5489\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/eetutor2018</a>"},{"pid":"c3c10c757ecb6c23c4fcaf5968285b75dabc5573","tid":721634,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T21:44:02.000Z","msg":"星期一至日呢學術顧問 <img src=